> Education, healthcare, and museums are all fair game to Christensen. This [lends nicely](https://link.morningbrew.com/click/31713240.358489/aHR0cHM6Ly9saW5rcy5tb3JuaW5nYnJldy5jb20vYy83TXI%5FbWJjaWQ9MzE3MTMyNDAuMzU4NDg5Jm1pZD1hN2EzMGZkMzMwOGQ5MThlOWJjZDYwYTcxOTM1NmE2NCZtYmxpZD02NDQ4N2JhYWRiY2U/647f57557909890704100155Baf8516cb) to top-down free markets over public goods‚Äîand taxpayers end up with subpar results.
